WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.000
Why do you need a music player in 2025?

2
00:00:03.000 --> 00:00:06.500
A player is compact. It is significantly lighter than a smartphone.

3
00:00:06.500 --> 00:00:09.500
And some models can be clipped onto your clothes.

4
00:00:09.500 --> 00:00:12.500
Music will keep playing even if the internet goes out.

5
00:00:12.500 --> 00:00:15.500
And in Michurinsk, that has been happening a lot lately.

6
00:00:15.500 --> 00:00:19.500
A player supports both wired and wireless headphones.

7
00:00:19.500 --> 00:00:22.500
Something modern smartphones can't boast about.

8
00:00:22.500 --> 00:00:25.500
But still, one question remains.
